00:02:25.676 --> 00:02:30.392
ikh, Yokheved Ayberman,

00:02:30.392 --> 00:02:38.731
geborn gevorn in tsvantsik zekstn yor.

00:02:38.731 --> 00:02:40.373
nu vos zol ikh nokh zogn?

00:02:40.373 --> 00:02:44.494
az az, der tate iz geven an arbeter.

00:02:44.494 --> 00:02:48.313
un di mame iz geven a, a shtub-froy.

00:02:48.313 --> 00:02:50.532
yeder tsvey yor flegt zi hobn a kind.

00:02:50.532 --> 00:02:52.751
di mame hot gehat zibn kinder.

00:02:52.751 --> 00:02:55.297
der tate hot oysgeboyt der shtub

00:02:55.297 --> 00:03:00.650
un, un er iz ibergegangen... mir zaynen ibergegangen in shtub.

00:03:00.650 --> 00:03:03.279
di, der lebn iz geven nit keyn gringer.

00:03:03.279 --> 00:03:05.093
ober vos?

00:03:05.093 --> 00:03:08.594
mit, ikh hob nit gefilt az imetser tshepet mir.

00:03:08.594 --> 00:03:11.601
ikh bin gek- gegangen in der yidisher shul,

00:03:11.601 --> 00:03:13.623
az ikh bin gevorn elter,

00:03:13.623 --> 00:03:18.635
un ikh hob zikh gekent firn vi a mentsh, vi ale mentshn in der velt.

00:03:18.635 --> 00:03:21.772
ikh hob gornisht nit gefilt keyn shlekhts.

00:03:21.772 --> 00:03:25.794
s'iz nit geven take, z-... der tate, er iz dokh geven der arbeter, take

00:03:25.794 --> 00:03:29.294
geven shver tsu dem ah onfirn mit der mishpokhe,

00:03:29.294 --> 00:03:31.193
ober vos?

00:03:31.193 --> 00:03:34.865
ikh hob nit gefilt, ot azoy darf dos zayn.

00:03:34.865 --> 00:03:38.715
 durkhgegangen dray yor in BET SEFER,

00:03:38.715 --> 00:03:40.731
a yidishe BET SEFER,

00:03:40.731 --> 00:03:44.496
geven dortn zeyer gut. ikh hob gefilt zikh azoy vi in shtub.

00:03:44.496 --> 00:03:47.698
vayl di gas undzere iz oykh geven a yidishe.

00:03:47.698 --> 00:03:52.915
un iber dray yor hot men undz ara- ibergegebn in a rusisher shul.

00:03:52.915 --> 00:03:55.025
di rusishe shul

00:03:55.025 --> 00:03:57.488
iz iz geven far mir fremd.

00:03:57.488 --> 00:04:01.531
vayl di gantse gas iz geven yidn, un in shtub hot men geredt oyf yidish.

00:04:01.531 --> 00:04:05.987
un in BET SEFER iz geven zeyer shver mir.

00:04:05.987 --> 00:04:13.275
ober fundestvegn hob ikh gelernt zikh a por yor, un se hot zikh ongehoybn di milkhome.

00:04:13.275 --> 00:04:16.225
ikh hob aykh gevolt fregn nokh far dem

00:04:16.225 --> 00:04:19.825
ye, nayn un draysikstn yor efsher.

00:04:19.825 --> 00:04:22.600
ikh hob aykh gevolt fregn a bisl nokh far dem

00:04:22.600 --> 00:04:28.478
ge- geleb- geborn gevorn un gelebt hot ir in Minsk unter der sovyetisher regirung, rikhtik?

00:04:27.050 --> 00:04:30.400
ye, unter der sovyetisher regirung.

00:04:30.400 --> 00:04:32.000
mir flegn, s- nu nu?

00:04:30.578 --> 00:04:31.388
vi

00:04:33.225 --> 00:04:35.150
vi hobn mir gelebt?

00:04:35.150 --> 00:04:37.650
vi hot ir gelebt hot ir mir dertseylt.

00:04:37.650 --> 00:04:43.950
keyn antisemitishkeyt spetsyel hot ir nisht gefilt dortn, far far ayere tsaytn, far, biz di milkhome iz oysgebrokhn.

00:04:43.950 --> 00:04:51.250
ikh hob nit gefilt. kh'hob gefilt az s'felt altsenesd-, ikh hob, s'hot gefelt altsenesding, ober ikh hob nit gefilt

00:04:51.250 --> 00:04:53.273
az es darf zayn beser.

00:04:53.273 --> 00:04:55.870
az mir flegn shteyn dortn bay nakht, avekgeyn

00:04:55.870 --> 00:05:00.375
far nemen a TOR O oyf nemen, a lebl broyt

00:05:00.375 --> 00:05:03.625
iz iz, hob ikh geklert ot azoy darf dos zayn.

00:05:03.625 --> 00:05:06.825
flegt men, fleg ikh, geven di eltste, fleg ikh avekgeyn

00:05:06.825 --> 00:05:09.600
un shteyn in otshered,

00:05:09.600 --> 00:05:12.553
un un dernokh bakumen a lebl broyt.

00:05:12.553 --> 00:05:17.371
un mit dem lebl broyt hob ikh, hob ikh kleyninke heringlekh, KAMSAH hot zikh dos gerufn,

00:05:17.371 --> 00:05:20.839
un az mir flegn shteyn in otshered nokh deroyf

00:05:20.839 --> 00:05:22.800
flegt men undz,

00:05:22.800 --> 00:05:25.675
flegn undz di kristn zogn "oyf vayter zayt ir do?"

00:05:25.675 --> 00:05:28.825
ikh hob nit farshtanen az zey meynen az dos iz a yid do.

00:05:28.825 --> 00:05:33.100
un ikh hob gelebt azoy fray, un mir iz geven gut.

00:05:33.198 --> 00:05:37.031
yetst hob ikh aykh gevolt fregn nokh a frage, mit ayer erloybenish.

00:05:37.031 --> 00:05:43.776
ir hot shoyn dermant az lebn di, lern- frier hot ir gelernt in a sovyetisher yidisher shk- shule,

00:05:42.825 --> 00:05:44.050
ye, ye.

00:05:44.050 --> 00:05:46.021
un in der heym hot men geredt yidish.

00:05:45.475 --> 00:05:47.525
ye, un di gas iz geven a yidishe.

00:05:46.361 --> 00:05:51.800
akhuts dem vos me fleg redn yidish in der heym, hot ir gevust a bisl vegn yidishkeyt?

00:05:51.800 --> 00:05:56.223
ir hot gehat a anung vegn a yontev, vegn a shabes, vos hot ir gevust in yene tsaytn?

00:05:54.125 --> 00:05:56.950
ikh farshtey, ikh farshtey. ikh farshtey vos ir fregt.

00:05:56.950 --> 00:06:01.775
mayn tate hot undz nit gestaret zikh dertseyln

00:06:01.775 --> 00:06:04.725
az mir zaynen yidn, mir darfn kenen

00:06:04.725 --> 00:06:07.468
di, di, ah, di TORA

00:06:07.468 --> 00:06:11.225
un mir darfn kenen visn, ober vos &lt;hot&gt; der tate flegt ton,

00:06:11.225 --> 00:06:12.660
er flegt davenen.

00:06:12.660 --> 00:06:17.125
er flegt onton, er flegt onton oyfn shtern a

00:06:17.125 --> 00:06:17.800
tfiln.

00:06:17.675 --> 00:06:20.911
tfiln, oyfn hant tfiln arumbindn,

00:06:20.911 --> 00:06:25.772
un onton dem tales, un az mir flegn im fregn, "tate, vos iz dos? tate, vos iz dos?"

00:06:25.772 --> 00:06:30.387
flegt er zogn, "she, shtil, shtil. ikh davn."

00:06:30.387 --> 00:06:36.283
ober vos dos iz, ven dos iz, vu dos iz, der tate hot nit derklert.

00:06:36.283 --> 00:06:40.069
dem, der tate hot dos nit farshtanen az me darf derklern.

00:06:40.069 --> 00:06:42.650
dos iz vos me tut hayntike yorn,

00:06:42.650 --> 00:06:49.650
az me zol derklern ver mir zaynen, vet efsher nit avekgeyn azoy fil mentshn in der erd.

00:06:49.650 --> 00:06:53.050
yetst hob ikh aykh gevolt nokh a frage fregn.

00:06:53.050 --> 00:06:56.525
in nayn un draysikstn yor iz oysgebrokhn di velt-milkhome.

00:06:56.525 --> 00:06:57.250
ye.

00:06:57.250 --> 00:07:01.625
hot ir dortn gev-, iz, lebndik in Rusland, in Sovyetn-Rusland,

00:07:01.625 --> 00:07:07.103
hot ir gevust vegn dem, az se brekht oys a milkhome, ir hot gevu- gehert epes vegn Hitlern, vegn zayn,

00:07:07.103 --> 00:07:10.700
vi er firt zikh gegn yidn, ir hot gehat epes a anung vegn dem?

00:07:10.700 --> 00:07:15.000
mayn tate iz avek in nayn un draysikstn yor, hot men im genumen oyf milkhome.

00:07:15.000 --> 00:07:17.325
der tate iz dortn geven.

00:07:17.325 --> 00:07:20.100
er flegt bre- er, iz er geven dortn.

00:07:20.100 --> 00:07:23.475
in a kurtser tsayt iz er gekumen tsurik.

00:07:23.475 --> 00:07:26.175
un er hot gezogt, "ikh veys? me lebt."

00:07:26.175 --> 00:07:29.600
dos iz geendikt. ober s'iz gekumen OLIM

00:07:29.600 --> 00:07:32.450
fun Rusland, fun Poyln, oyf Rusland,

00:07:32.450 --> 00:07:35.525
un zey hobn undz ongehoybn dertseyln vos der daytsh hot...

00:07:35.525 --> 00:07:37.825
geven dortn shoyn in Poyln,

00:07:37.825 --> 00:07:42.000
un di poylishe un di, un di daytshn hobn shoyn, NEGED di yidn.

00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:45.875
ober mir hobn nit gekent farshteyn, vos iz dos "NEGED di yidn"?

00:07:45.875 --> 00:07:49.850
un zey dertseyln, az me, az me khapt zey, me shlogt zey,

00:07:49.850 --> 00:07:53.675
me shist zey, hobn mir oyf zey gekukt azoy vi oyf meshugoim.

00:07:53.675 --> 00:07:57.625
mir hobn nit farshtanen. mir hobn geklert, "vos dertseyln zey bikhlal?"

00:07:57.625 --> 00:07:59.675
dos iz, dos iz nito...

00:07:59.675 --> 00:08:01.425
dos flegn dertseyln di bezhenikes.

00:08:00.470 --> 00:08:03.543
vegn vos tsu der-, di bezhentses flegn dertseyln,

00:08:03.543 --> 00:08:07.434
un mir hobn zey ni-, mir hobn nit farshtanen vos tsu gleybn.

00:08:07.102 --> 00:08:07.941
ikh farshtey.

00:08:07.434 --> 00:08:10.200
dos iz geven in nayn un draysikstn yor.

00:08:10.200 --> 00:08:13.946
yetst, dos lebn tsit zikh azoy biz eyn un fertsik. vos pasir-?

00:08:13.223 --> 00:08:15.510
dos, ye, ye.

00:08:14.050 --> 00:08:16.914
vos pasirt in eyn un fertsikstn yor, bite?

00:08:15.825 --> 00:08:20.300
dos iz, fi- firt zikh bizkl eyn un fertsikstn yor,

00:08:20.300 --> 00:08:23.300
eyn un fertsikstn yor, zumerdike tsaytn,

00:08:23.300 --> 00:08:31.100
der tate mayner dertseylt undz az s'geyt, az s'heybt zikh on di milkhome.

00:08:31.100 --> 00:08:32.775
tate gekumen aheym

00:08:32.775 --> 00:08:36.275
un er zogt, "efsher veln mir aroysforn fun danet.

00:08:36.275 --> 00:08:39.550
vayl di di daytshn kenen alts opton."

00:08:39.550 --> 00:08:45.575
ober di, ober di, s'iz bay undz geven zeks kinder, un di mame iz geve- a shvanger froy.

00:08:45.575 --> 00:08:49.725
me hot zikh gedreyt aher, me hot zikh gedreyt ahin, un, me hot gereshet az dos toyg nit.

00:08:49.725 --> 00:08:53.275
dos toyg nit aroysgeyn, vayl mit azoy fil kinder.

00:08:53.275 --> 00:08:57.150
un m'iz geblibn in, far di daytshn.

00:08:57.150 --> 00:09:02.025
der, der oylem hot hot zikh, gekent zikh zukhn vos tsu esn,

00:09:02.025 --> 00:09:07.800
di ershte tsayt, vos s'iz geblibn in di kromen, flegt men hobn gelt, yeder flegt nemen aheym altsenesding.

00:09:07.800 --> 00:09:11.827
ot azoy hobn mir oykh geton. ikh hob dos geton.

00:09:11.827 --> 00:09:16.722
un bizkl vanen mir zaynen arayngegangen, bizkl vanen di daytshn zaynen

00:09:16.722 --> 00:09:21.713
aropgelozn zikh, un di rusishe hobn undz opgeshtupt fun zikh,

00:09:21.713 --> 00:09:25.711
un me hot undz gezogt az me geyt boyen a geto.

00:09:25.711 --> 00:09:29.350
vos geto? ven geto? ver geto? ver veys?

00:09:29.350 --> 00:09:33.775
mir hobn gezen ober me hot gefirt di rusishe PLENNe, hot men zey oyfn veg geshosn,

00:09:33.775 --> 00:09:35.600
me hot zey gefirt kilometers,

00:09:35.600 --> 00:09:40.125
un me flegt, eyner flegt betn epes trinken vaser, flegt men im shisn.

00:09:40.125 --> 00:09:43.000
dernokh hot men geheysn di yidn aroysgeyn fun,

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:46.025
di mener aroysgeyn fun ge- fun

00:09:46.025 --> 00:09:49.625
fun, nokh di geto boyt zikh, aroysgeyn fun geto.

00:09:49.625 --> 00:09:54.800
un un avekgeyn in a lager, un dortn iz geven di rusishe PLENNe,

00:09:54.800 --> 00:09:59.400
di ale, un di, di mener di rusishe,

00:09:59.400 --> 00:10:01.300
un di, un di yidn.

00:10:01.300 --> 00:10:07.525
in eyn gutn tog iber a kurtser tsayt hot men geheysn az di yidn zoln opgeyn in eyn zayt.

00:10:07.525 --> 00:10:10.850
un di rusn, di PLENNe, zoln zayn in a tsveytn zayt.

00:10:10.850 --> 00:10:15.425
un dernokh hot men gefregt, "un ver iz WOLGADEUTSCHEn?"

00:10:15.425 --> 00:10:18.000
hobn zikh oyfgehoybn der WOLGADEUTSCH

00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:20.500
un zikh, un zey geheysn opgeyn.

00:10:20.500 --> 00:10:23.025
un ver zaynen di rusishe?

00:10:23.025 --> 00:10:26.850
 ah, a driter plats.

00:10:26.850 --> 00:10:30.875
iz ot azoy hot men zikh tseteylt. m'iz geven lebn taykh,

00:10:30.875 --> 00:10:34.400
un me hot zey nit gelozn trinken, me flegt zey shisn.

00:10:34.400 --> 00:10:39.000
dos iz geven der daytshishe gang.

00:10:39.000 --> 00:10:44.725
un dernokh hobn di WOLGADEUTSCHEn farkh- farnumen dem plats,

00:10:44.725 --> 00:10:47.775
un zey zaynen glaykh ongehoybn hitn

00:10:47.775 --> 00:10:53.700
hitn di, de- de- dem plats, hitn di W- di JUDEN.

00:10:53.700 --> 00:10:55.675
di rusishe di PLENNe,

00:10:55.675 --> 00:11:00.225
hobn shoyn dem yidn oykh nit gelozn durkhgeyn, zey flegn fun im raysn.

00:11:00.225 --> 00:11:06.225
in a kurtser tsayt arum, iber etlekhe vokhn, az der, yidn hobn gelitn

00:11:06.225 --> 00:11:08.950
un mir kinder flegn avektrogn ahin esn,

00:11:08.950 --> 00:11:14.425
un, un, bizkl vanen di di yidn hot men tsugenumen in turme.

00:11:14.425 --> 00:11:18.100
di yidn zaynen geven in turme.

00:11:18.100 --> 00:11:21.225
un zey hobn dortn gut tsugelitn zeks vokhn,

00:11:21.225 --> 00:11:22.650
un me hot zey opgelozn aheym.

00:11:22.650 --> 00:11:26.400
ober zey zaynen avek. ober vos hobn zey geton, di daytshn?

00:11:26.400 --> 00:11:30.025
zey hobn aropgenumen di inteligentsye fun dem yidishn folk.

00:11:30.025 --> 00:11:32.500
me hot gelozn aheym di arbeter.

00:11:32.500 --> 00:11:33.975
me hot gelozn di, aheym

00:11:33.975 --> 00:11:38.425
 oto di vos zey zaynen nit keyn, nit keyn farshpitste.

00:11:38.425 --> 00:11:41.075
un ot hot men undz genumen in geto.

00:11:41.075 --> 00:11:42.075
vos hot men...

00:11:41.136 --> 00:11:44.867
gemakht shoyn mit di geto, hobn mir, zey hobn geheysn

00:11:44.867 --> 00:11:49.801
zayn in geto, un mir hobn nit di rekht aroysgeyn oyfn rusishn rayon,

00:11:49.801 --> 00:11:54.412
un, un, un, un di politsyantn vern di, rusn

00:11:54.412 --> 00:11:57.069
un di WOLGADEUTSCHEn.

00:11:57.069 --> 00:12:00.750
un mir yidn zaynen in geto.

00:12:00.750 --> 00:12:03.450
vos hot pasirt mit di yidishe inteligentsye?

00:12:03.450 --> 00:12:08.475
di yidishe tel- inteligentsye, di mener vos zaynen geven in turme, me hot aropgenumen.

00:12:08.475 --> 00:12:12.400
azoy vi me nemt aropet fun sm-, fun zoyermilkh di smetene,

00:12:12.400 --> 00:12:16.050
hot men zey aropgenumen, me hot zey aropgenumen, s'iz geblibn zoyermilkh.

00:12:16.050 --> 00:12:17.638
m'hot zey tse- oysgeharget.

00:12:17.150 --> 00:12:18.750
me hot zey, me hot zey

00:12:18.750 --> 00:12:22.746
 me hot zey, zey, mir bey- me, zey zaynen nito,

00:12:22.746 --> 00:12:26.060
fun di teg vos me hot zey tsugenumen zaynen zey nito.

00:12:26.060 --> 00:12:27.474
AD HAYOM.

00:12:29.700 --> 00:12:37.266
yetst mi- vos far a gzeyres flegn zey onmakhn? me hot aykh arayngefirt in geto. vos nokh far a tsores hobn zey ongemakht demolts in yene tsaytn?

00:12:35.975 --> 00:12:38.350
ah...

00:12:38.350 --> 00:12:42.475
un mir hobn nokh nokh nit farshtanen vos me geyt undz makhn.

00:12:42.475 --> 00:12:45.525
un vos mir boyen far zikh aleyn.

00:12:45.525 --> 00:12:48.125
ah, un un mir zaynen in geto,

00:12:48.125 --> 00:12:52.091
eyder di, eyder s'iz geven der ershter pogrom hot men bay mayn shvesterkind

00:12:52.091 --> 00:12:54.329
alemen oysgekoylet in shtub.

00:12:54.329 --> 00:12:57.627
m'iz ge-, m'iz zey IZNASILevet.

00:12:57.627 --> 00:13:02.895
me hot der meydl fun draytsn yor aropgerisn di vayse herelekh ire, di tsep.

00:13:02.895 --> 00:13:06.209
un me hot ir oyfn bet tseshnitn di KHAZE,

00:13:06.209 --> 00:13:08.075
un, un, di GRUD'.

00:13:08.075 --> 00:13:12.450
un der tsveyter shvester, eyn un tsvantsik yor, hot men ir oykh di zelbe zakh geton.

00:13:12.450 --> 00:13:17.200
un azoy hot men oysgeharget in shtub a, a fertsn mentshn.

00:13:17.200 --> 00:13:21.175
un di mame iz gelegn zeyere, mit fun eyn zayt

00:13:21.175 --> 00:13:26.775
halt zi eyn kind, un fun tsveytn zayt halt zi dem eynikl, un di bobe ligt a, a

