bay di, dos vos ikh hob frier dertseylt, iz dos geven in a shtub.

00:14:10.200 --> 00:14:15.525
ober dos iz geven hunderter, toyznter yidn zaynen gegangen in a kolone.

00:14:15.525 --> 00:14:22.900
ikh hob gegangen brengen aheym epes. zakhn, esnvarg.

