un ikh hob derzen az s'firt zikh a kolone yidn,

00:14:26.225 --> 00:14:27.925
a groyse kolone,

00:14:27.925 --> 00:14:31.975
f- fun, fun onheyb gas un tsum sof gas ze ikh, der sof gas,

