un zey hobn oyfgeklibn dos vos di yidn hobn ongehoybn fanandervarfn, zey hobn ongehoybn farshteyn

00:15:34.621 --> 00:15:36.378
vuhin me firt zey.

00:15:36.378 --> 00:15:40.189
un azoy hot men oysgeharget gasn, gantse gasn,

00:15:40.189 --> 00:15:44.243
oto dos vos ikh dertseyl aykh fun dem ershtn pogrom.

