 mit, nokh a meydele, zaynen mir avekgegangen, dortn ire kroyvim geven.

00:16:53.107 --> 00:16:54.296
gekumen ahin,

00:16:54.296 --> 00:16:57.729
zog ikh, ikh zi- ze bay zey reyn,

