un mir hobn gezen, un mir hobn ge-, un mir hobn geklert:

00:17:14.269 --> 00:17:18.756
nu, fun dort-, fu-, vi geyt men avek ergets in vald?

00:17:18.756 --> 00:17:22.404
ober s'iz geven shney, s'iz geven nokh farfrorn alts.

