un, un mir hobn gereshet az mir geyen tsurik in geto.

00:17:25.945 --> 00:17:28.351
in Minsker geto.

00:17:28.351 --> 00:17:31.702
az ikh bin gekumen aheym, dertseylt vos ikh hob gezen,

00:17:31.702 --> 00:17:33.810
di khevre, der in shtub

00:17:33.810 --> 00:17:36.621
hobn khevre avekgegangen ahin,

00:17:36.621 --> 00:17:38.405
fun gas, khevre,

00:17:38.405 --> 00:17:42.324
hern un zen un a kuk ton, un efsher aher un efsher ahin,

00:17:42.324 --> 00:17:44.702
un zey zaynen dortn geven etlekhe teg,

00:17:44.702 --> 00:17:46.053
un s'iz gevorn a pogrom.

00:17:46.053 --> 00:17:48.863
m'hot zey ale, di gantse shtetl oysgeharget.

00:17:48.863 --> 00:17:49.687
dortn.

00:17:48.989 --> 00:17:51.053
dos iz geven in Novedranke.

00:17:51.053 --> 00:17:53.215
in shtetl vu ikh bin frier geven.

