un s'iz gevorn do bay un- di, DESANTNIKes,

00:18:20.175 --> 00:18:22.809
di daytshishe vos zey hobn zikh bay undz aropgelozn,

00:18:22.809 --> 00:18:24.053
ho-, flegn undz,

00:18:24.053 --> 00:18:27.648
zey flegn undz aher ahin firn far di nezer,

00:18:27.648 --> 00:18:29.107
zey hobn undz,

00:18:29.107 --> 00:18:31.837
mir hobn nit gevust oyf velkher velt mir zaynen, mir hobn nit gevust

00:18:31.837 --> 00:18:34.431
vos mir zaynen, vos vet zayn, vi vet zayn,

00:18:34.431 --> 00:18:36.485
un ver vet onfirn mit deroyf.

00:18:36.485 --> 00:18:38.864
un di rusishe zaynen antlofn.

00:18:38.864 --> 00:18:45.254
di, di, m- di, di, di VOYENNY, di VOYENNY zaynen antlofn, di militsye iz tsegangen.

