un zey zaynen geven azoy vi, azoy vi,

00:19:02.479 --> 00:19:04.472
erger fun hint.

00:19:04.472 --> 00:19:08.080
a hunt ken nokh nemen a bisl vaser, un dos hot men nit gekent oykhet.

00:19:08.080 --> 00:19:11.848
azoy arum hobn mir ongehoybn zen, ikh hob ongehoybn farshteyn.

00:19:11.848 --> 00:19:15.186
ober ikh bin nit geven zikher,

00:19:15.186 --> 00:19:18.328
hob ikh nit gezen, nit geven zikher

00:19:18.328 --> 00:19:21.102
az - vos vet zayn?

00:19:21.102 --> 00:19:22.926
iz ot vil ikh zogn,

00:19:22.926 --> 00:19:26.638
az farshtanen, hob ikh ongehoybn farshteyn in tsvey un fertsikstn yor.

00:19:26.638 --> 00:19:29.256
iber a halb yor vos s'iz forgekumen.

00:19:29.256 --> 00:19:34.165
ikh hob shoyn ongehoybn zukhn vos zol men ton.

00:19:34.165 --> 00:19:37.002
ober, vos zol men ton?

00:19:37.002 --> 00:19:39.264
az, az s'iz nito vuhin tsu avektsugeyn.

00:19:39.264 --> 00:19:40.985
s'iz nito vos tsu ton.

00:19:40.985 --> 00:19:43.499
un mit di khavertes reydn mir,

00:19:43.499 --> 00:19:46.107
un mit di khaveyrim, un me redt.

00:19:46.107 --> 00:19:47.675
un dos iz dos.

00:19:47.675 --> 00:19:53.675
me, ikh zukh a veg oyf lebn blaybn.

00:19:53.675 --> 00:19:56.525
un vos ikh'l kenen, vemen ikh'l kenen, vu ikh'l kenen,

00:19:56.525 --> 00:20:00.919
vel ikh zukhn oyf rateven.

00:20:00.919 --> 00:20:03.696
un ot azoy zaynen mir gelebt.

00:20:03.696 --> 00:20:05.270
mit khavertes geredt.

00:20:05.270 --> 00:20:08.108
mit khaveyrim geredt.

00:20:08.108 --> 00:20:10.432
mir zaynen dernokh aroysgegangen,

00:20:10.432 --> 00:20:13.378
kh'hob gehat a fet- tsvey feters.

