m'iz aropge- ikh hob tsugeforn tsum TSHERVENSKOM mark, tsugegangen, gegangen, un gezen zey,

00:21:43.151 --> 00:21:45.972
fun hintn, un altsenesding iz zeyer sheyn, zeyer fayn.

